ictk.boardgame.chess.net.ics.event

Interface ICSEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ANSIConsole, ICSBoardManager, ICSGameAdapter

    public interface ICSEventListener
    Implement this interface to receive events from the server. The object must also tell the ICSRouter which events it would like to be notified about.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void icsEventDispatched(ICSEvent evt)
      When an event is received by the ICSRouter and this object is on the Listener list, this method will be called.
